{
  "title": "Maxema - Kind - Personalized and promotional pens. Promotional writing instruments and custom printed pens.",
  "description": "Kind Kind is our pen in R-PET, recyclable and refillable. Designed to convey a message with a strong visual impact and low environmental impact. The material from which it is made is obtained by gathering and recycling PET, the most commonly used polyester in the production of soft-drink bottles. Graceful lines, an iconic profile and plenty of room for customisation. Kind is available in 23 colours, 3 finishes and 5 combinations.",
