  "mainText": "Italiano English Reserved Area Contacts Company Pens Customisation Sample kits Finishes Recycled pens More maxema ® via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com P PRODUCTS Our pens Kind / Kind / Icon Pure / Flow Pure / Dot / Zink / Pixel / Bay / Mood Metal / Kind / Mood / Flow / View / Tag Green / Next / Tag / Icon / Icon green / Ethic Search by color rose/purple azure / blue green yellow/orange red cream/brown grey black white select a color S Services customisation packaging pantone colors sample kits C COMPANY Maxema Company contacts FAVORITES SAMPLE KITS ACCOUNT FAQ MEDIA DISCLAIMER previous model/ next model HomePens Catalogue Kind Kind Message from a bottle. Technical information Download pdfof this model Kind is our pen in R-PET, recyclable and refillable. Designed to convey a message with a strong visual impact and low environmental impact. The material from which it is made is obtained by gathering and recycling PET, the most commonly used polyester in the production of soft-drink bottles. Graceful lines, an iconic profile and plenty of room for customisation. Kind is available in 23 colours, 3 finishes and 5 combinations. 1/4 Details 2/4 Variants 3/4 Technical information 4/4 Customisations log in P/Kind 1/4 Details Details of the pen Our first pen in certified R-PET, made of plastic from recycled bottles. Smooth design, gentle impact. Clean the planet, colour your world. 2/4 Models and colors Available in 5 models and 57 color variants K1 - K1 MATT CB RP Show details add to favorites Solid colour barrel with matt finish, solid matt white colour clip and push-button. K1 - K1 MATT RP Show details add to favorites Solid colours with matt finish. K1 - K1 GOM MATT CB RP Show details add to favorites Solid colour barrel with rubber finish, solid white colour clip and push button. K1 - K1 GOM MATT RP Show details add to favorites Solid colour barrel with rubber finish, solid colour clip and push button with matt finish. K1 - K1 FROST RP Show details add to favorites Transparent colours with matt finish. 3/4 Technical information Print areas and tech specs Features ● retractable ● made of certified R-PET derived from the recycling of plastic bottles ● Jumbo refill, blue and black ink ● the barrel is available in matt and rubber finishes, the clip and the pushbutton are available in matt finish ● rubberised barrel versions (GOM) are only printable on the clip Modularity you can combine differently coloured parts from the same version (or code number), or elements from different versions A Push-button B Clip C Barrel Print areas 1 pad printing 50 x 9 mm* 2 pad printing 32 x 7 mm 3 screen printing 40 x 30 mm* * Not available for the following versions: - K1-GOM MATT RP - K1-GOM MATT CB RP 4/4 Customisations The brands mentioned in this catalogue are the exclusive property of the respective owners. They are used for purely illustrative purposes and cannot be the object of any buying and selling transactions, under any circumstances. via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com MAXEMA SRL P.IVA 05321380015 privacy policy var acceptText='Accetto'; var policy_url='/cookie_privacy_policy/en'; var cookie_message='Il sito www.maxema.com utilizza cookie esclusivamente tecnici per permettere una corretta navigazione e la completa fruizione di tutti i contenuti da parte dell\\'utente. Non utilizziamo in alcun modo cookie di profilazione.'; var acceptText='I Understand'; var policy_url='/cookie_privacy_policy/en'; var cookie_message='This site uses cookies to improve their services and experience of readers. If you decide to continue browsing we consider that you accept their use.'; $(document).ready(function(){ $.cookieBar({ message: cookie_message, acceptButton: true, acceptText: acceptText, policyButton: true, policyText: 'Privacy Policy', policyURL: policy_url, autoEnable: true, acceptOnCo